---
config:
    layout: elk
---
graph LR
    A["📄 Input Files<br/>(.drawio, .solution)"] 
    
    A -->|Parser| B["RawModelData<br/><<type>><br/>string"]
    
    B -->|Builder| C["UMLGraph<br/>- ID<br/>- Nodes: UMLNode[]<br/>- Edges: UMLEdge[]"]
    
    C -->|Split| D["Two Parallel Paths"]
    
    D -->|Student Path| E["ProcessedUMLGraph<br/>- ID<br/>- Nodes: ProcessedNode[]<br/>- Edges: ProcessedEdge[]<br/>⚡ 1 name per attribute/method"]
    
    D -->|Solution Path| F["SolutionProcessedUMLGraph<br/>- ID<br/>- Nodes: SolutionProcessedNode[]<br/>- ScoreConfig<br/>🔥 OR-aware aliases<br/>A|B|C format"]
    
    E -->|Matcher Input| G["ProcessedNode<br/>- NodeID<br/>- ClassName<br/>- Attributes[]<br/>- Methods[]"]
    
    F -->|Matcher Input| H["SolutionProcessedNode<br/>- NodeID<br/>- ClassNames: A|B|C<br/>- Attributes[]<br/>- Methods[]"]
    
    G -->|3-Tier Match<br/>Arch→Fuzzy→Delta| I["MappingTable<br/>map[SolNodeID]MappedNode<br/>- StudentID<br/>- Similarity: float64"]
    
    H -->|Comparator Input| I
    E -->|Comparator Input| I
    F -->|Comparator Input| I
    
    I -->|Deep Diff| J["DiffReport<br/>📌 MissingDetail<br/>❌ WrongDetail<br/>➕ ExtraDetail<br/>✅ CorrectDetail"]
    
    J -->|Grading| K["GradeResult<br/>- TotalScore<br/>- CorrectPercent<br/>- Feedbacks[]<br/>- Report<br/>- SolutionGraph<br/>- StudentGraph"]
    
    K -->|Split| L["Output Stage"]
    
    L -->|Reporter| M1["CSV Report<br/>student_name,score,percent"]
    L -->|Visualizer| M2["HTML Report<br/>🎨 Interactive<br/>SVG Icons<br/>Color Coded"]
    L -->|GUI| M3["Desktop App<br/>Display Results<br/>Export HTML"]
    
